Privacy Policy
We take the privacy of the information you send us seriously. Below describes what and how the data you provide
        us
        is used when you use the app Windometer.
App Permissions
LOCATION
While using the app, and given your consent, your device location is used to obtain real-time weather data.
Analytics
The app collects analytics to improve the app and monitor usage trends. This includes device OS version, app
        version, crash reports, search queries and usage data. We never store your name, phone number or contact
        information unless you voluntarily provide this to us.
If you have any comments, please email privacy[ at ]frostedapps.com.